# Binance FUTURES DEMO credentials — copy to .env.binance-testnet and fill in.
# Generate these at https://testnet.binancefuture.com :
#   1. Open https://testnet.binancefuture.com and log in (GitHub or email — no KYC).
#   2. You start with a demo balance of play money (USDT).
#   3. Bottom of the page → "API Key" tab → copy the API Key and Secret Key.
#      (If none exists, it shows one on first visit / lets you generate it.)
# NOTE: ccxt deprecated the old testnet sandbox; the bot routes these keys to the
# DEMO endpoint (demo-fapi.binance.com) via enable_demo_trading — same keys work.
# These keys ONLY work against the demo environment — they cannot touch real funds.
FREQTRADE__EXCHANGE__KEY=your_binance_testnet_key_here
FREQTRADE__EXCHANGE__SECRET=your_binance_testnet_secret_here
